@startuml YuPeiyuanDetail
title 虞沛远 yupeiyuan：角色权限、好友与私聊完整类关系

top to bottom direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultFontName Microsoft YaHei
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam nodesep 55
skinparam ranksep 55
hide empty members
hide circle

skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor<<Controller>> #E8F3FF
  BackgroundColor<<Service>> #EAF7EA
  BackgroundColor<<Mapper>> #FFF4D8
  BackgroundColor<<Entity>> #F7F7F7
  BackgroundColor<<DTO>> #F4EAFE
  BackgroundColor<<Utility>> #F2F2F2
  BackgroundColor<<External>> #FFFFFF
}

legend right
  虞沛远负责：权限位定义、角色管理、成员角色分配、好友申请处理和私聊频道创建。
endlegend

package "虞沛远负责包 com.hive.yupeiyuan" as YPY #FFF4D8 {
  class "FriendController（好友接口）" as FriendController <<Controller>>
  class "DmController（私聊接口）" as DmController <<Controller>>
  class "RoleController（角色接口）" as RoleController <<Controller>>

  class "FriendService（好友私聊业务）" as FriendService <<Service>>
  class "RoleService（角色业务）" as RoleService <<Service>>
  class "PermissionService（权限校验）" as PermissionService <<Service>>
  class "Permissions（权限位常量）" as Permissions <<Utility>>

  interface "FriendshipMapper（好友关系表）" as FriendshipMapper <<Mapper>>
  interface "RoleMapper（角色表）" as RoleMapper <<Mapper>>
  interface "MemberRoleMapper（成员角色表）" as MemberRoleMapper <<Mapper>>

  class "Friendship（好友关系实体）" as Friendship <<Entity>>
  class "Role（角色实体）" as Role <<Entity>>
  class "MemberRole（成员角色实体）" as MemberRole <<Entity>>

  class "FriendVO（好友响应）" as FriendVO <<DTO>>
  class "FriendRequestVO（好友申请响应）" as FriendRequestVO <<DTO>>
  class "DmVO（私聊响应）" as DmVO <<DTO>>
  class "RoleReq（角色请求）" as RoleReq <<DTO>>
  class "RoleVO（角色响应）" as RoleVO <<DTO>>
}

package "外部依赖：张致硕 zhangzhishuo" as ZZS_EXT #E8F3FF {
  class ApiResponse <<External>>
  class BizException <<External>>
  interface HiveMapper <<External>>
  interface HiveMemberMapper <<External>>
  class Hive <<External>>
  class HiveMember <<External>>
}

package "外部依赖：张凯文 zhangkaiwen" as ZKW_EXT #EAF7EA {
  interface ChannelMapper <<External>>
  interface ChannelMemberMapper <<External>>
  class Channel <<External>>
  class WsPush <<External>>
}

package "外部依赖：江民智 jiangminzhi" as JMZ_EXT #F4EAFE {
  annotation CurrentUid
  interface UserMapper <<External>>
  class UserService <<External>>
  class User <<External>>
  class UserVO <<External>>
  class "AppEvents.FriendAccepted" as FriendAcceptedEvent <<External>>
}

FriendController ..> ApiResponse
DmController ..> ApiResponse
RoleController ..> ApiResponse
FriendController ..> CurrentUid
DmController ..> CurrentUid
RoleController ..> CurrentUid

FriendController --> FriendService : 好友接口
DmController --> FriendService : 私聊接口
FriendService --> FriendshipMapper : 好友关系持久化
FriendService --> ChannelMemberMapper : 私聊成员
FriendService --> ChannelMapper : 私聊频道
FriendService --> UserMapper : 用户查询
FriendService --> UserService : 用户资料
FriendService --> WsPush : 好友私聊通知
FriendService ..> BizException
FriendService ..> Channel
FriendService ..> User
FriendService ..> UserVO
FriendService ..> FriendAcceptedEvent : 发布
FriendService ..> FriendVO
FriendService ..> FriendRequestVO
FriendService ..> DmVO

RoleController --> RoleService : 角色接口
RoleService --> RoleMapper : 角色持久化
RoleService --> MemberRoleMapper : 成员角色分配
RoleService --> PermissionService : 管理角色权限
RoleService --> WsPush : 角色变更通知
RoleService ..> BizException
RoleService ..> RoleReq
RoleService ..> RoleVO

PermissionService --> HiveMapper : 蜂巢归属
PermissionService --> HiveMemberMapper : 成员身份
PermissionService --> RoleMapper : 有效权限
PermissionService ..> BizException
PermissionService ..> Hive
PermissionService ..> HiveMember
PermissionService ..> Permissions : 权限位规则

FriendshipMapper ..> Friendship
FriendshipMapper ..> FriendVO
FriendshipMapper ..> FriendRequestVO
RoleMapper ..> Role
RoleMapper ..> RoleVO
MemberRoleMapper ..> MemberRole

@enduml
